  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>負けちゃったし、しょうがないね。
このミソは普通に食べる事にするよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We lost, so I guess there's nothing we can do
about it. We'll just have to eat the miso like normal.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今日の夕飯は
焼き鳥丼とおみそ汁に決まりね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then tonight's dinner is decided.
Grilled chicken rice bowls and miso soup.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でもいっぱいミソ買っちゃったし
しばらくは毎日おみそ汁かも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I ended up buying a whole lot of miso though,
so we might having it every day for a while.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫！
おみそ汁もおいしいけど
ミソは直接なにかに塗ってもおいしいから！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's fine! Miso soup is delicious, but miso
spread directly onto something is delicious, too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>パンにでも野菜にでも
どんどんミソ塗っちゃえばいいよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whether it's bread, vegetables, or anything else,
spreading miso on it tastes great!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え、それは……ないなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uh, that's... gonna be a no from me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんで！？
身体には塗ろうとしてたのに！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why?! Are you planning on
covering your body with it?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>身体には塗っていいのに
パンはイヤなんて
女の子って不思議だなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine to cover your body in it, but it's
no good on bread? Girls are so odd.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
